## 2. Component Library

### Location
UI components are in `/components/ui/` following the **shadcn/ui** pattern.

### Available Components

| Component | File | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| `Button` | `button.tsx` | Multi-variant button with CVA |
| `Card` | `card.tsx` | Card container with header/content/footer |
| `Input` | `input.tsx` | Text input field |
| `Badge` | `badge.tsx` | Status badges |
| `Dialog` | `dialog.tsx` | Modal dialogs |
| `DropdownMenu` | `dropdown-menu.tsx` | Dropdown menus |
| `Select` | `select.tsx` | Select inputs |
| `Collapsible` | `collapsible.tsx` | Expandable sections |
| `Tooltip` | `tooltip.tsx` | Hover tooltips |
| `Avatar` | `avatar.tsx` | User avatars |
| `Separator` | `separator.tsx` | Divider lines |
| `Sidebar` | `sidebar.tsx` | App sidebar |
| `Sheet` | `sheet.tsx` | Slide-out panels |
| `Skeleton` | `skeleton.tsx` | Loading placeholders |
| `Breadcrumb` | `breadcrumb.tsx` | Navigation breadcrumbs |
| `Textarea` | `textarea.tsx` | Multi-line text input |
| `Label` | `label.tsx` | Form labels |

### Component Architecture Pattern

Components use **Class Variance Authority (CVA)** for variants:

```tsx
// Pattern: /components/ui/button.tsx
import { cva, type VariantProps } from "class-variance-authority"
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"

const buttonVariants = cva(
  "base-classes-here",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: "bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90",
        secondary: "bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80",
        ghost: "hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground",
        destructive: "bg-destructive text-white hover:bg-destructive/90",
        outline: "border bg-background shadow-xs hover:bg-accent",
        link: "text-primary underline-offset-4 hover:underline",
      },
      size: {
        default: "h-9 px-4 py-2",
        sm: "h-8 px-3",
        lg: "h-10 px-6",
        icon: "size-9",
        "icon-sm": "size-8",
        "icon-lg": "size-10",
      },
    },
    defaultVariants: {
      variant: "default",
      size: "default",
    },
  }
)

function Button({ className, variant, size, ...props }) {
  return (
    <button
      className={cn(buttonVariants({ variant, size, className }))}
      {...props}
    />
  )
}
```

### Creating New Components

1. Create file in `/components/ui/` or `/components/[feature]/`
2. Use `"use client"` directive if component has interactivity
3. Import `cn` from `@/lib/utils`
4. Use CVA for variants when needed
5. Compose from existing Radix primitives when possible

